	   <tr><td colspan=2>Wouldn't stamina only be of more use than strength if you are planning on soloing alot? I always understood that post lvl 20 soloing for a monk is a really tough job (especially with all the down time binding wounds, etc.) For soloing I could see why you would want the highest hp possible. But as part of a team the monks main job is to deal massive amounts of damage as quickly ass possible. <br><br>The healer classes are there to make sure you don't go too low on health and to buff you. So <br>how uninportant is strength? Is the stamina over strength arguement mainly because stamina gear is harder to come by then strength gear?<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
