	   <tr><td colspan=2>Stamina is above all else for the Monk, and it's not just a soloing issue. You are going to be relied upon to pull for your group on occassion and besides resists, HP means <i>everything</i>. Always dedicate your Monk to AC and HP.<br>&nbsp;<br>**********************************<br>"<span style='color: red;'>Man who goes to bed with itchy bum, wakes with smelly fingers.</span style='color: red;'>"</td></tr>
